<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
  <div
    class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-700"
  >
    <div class="h-3 bg-secondary"></div>
    <div class="p-8">
      <div
        class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary/10 dark:bg-secondary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-secondary"
      >
        <i class="material-icons text-4xl">person_add</i>
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-3 tracking-tight"
      >
        Nuevo Ingreso
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Si eres aspirante y deseas formar parte de nuestra comunidad
        universitaria, inicia aquí tu proceso de pre-registro y entrega de
        documentos.
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
          <i class="material-icons text-green-500 text-lg mr-2">check_circle</i>
          Convocatoria 2024-2025
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
          <i class="material-icons text-green-500 text-lg mr-2">check_circle</i>
          Guía de pre-registro
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        class="block w-full text-center bg-secondary text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >
        INICIAR INSCRIPCIÓN
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-700"
  >
    <div class="h-3 bg-primary"></div>
    <div class="p-8">
      <div
        class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 dark:bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary"
      >
        <i class="material-icons text-4xl">autorenew</i>
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary dark:text-white mb-3 tracking-tight"
      >
        Reinscripción
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Para alumnos regulares que continúan sus estudios en el siguiente
