      </p>
      <ul class="mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
          <i class="material-icons text-primary text-lg mr-2">event</i>
          Periodo: Mayo - Agosto
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
          <i class="material-icons text-primary text-lg mr-2">payment</i>
          Pago referenciado disponible
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        class="block w-full text-center bg-primary text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >
        ACCESO ALUMNOS
      </a>
    </div>
